  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Combine seitan, almond milk, bay leaves, salt, pepper, cumin seeds, and coriander powder in a large pot.",
    "Bring to boil over medium-high heat. Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for about 2 hours or until the liquid is absorbed and the dish has a nutty texture.",
    "Remove from heat and discard bay leaves. Serve hot as a vegan-friendly salt cod delight."
